All the restaurant staff is on edge, some
are about to get the axe, while others

2
00:00:04.770 --> 00:00:06.100 
might climb the corporate ladder.

3
00:00:06.690 --> 00:00:08.520 
No one in the whole place knows their

4
00:00:08.530 --> 00:00:09.380 
destiny for certain.

5
00:00:09.890 --> 00:00:12.500 
Some are jumping for joy, others are

6
00:00:12.510 --> 00:00:15.440 
biting their nails, and a few are already
in tears.

7
00:00:16.050 --> 00:00:19.920 
They all know they were put under the
microscope, but what they don't know is

8
00:00:19.930 --> 00:00:20.800 
how they were judged.

9
00:00:21.110 --> 00:00:23.320 
It was a hush -hush evaluation.

10
00:00:23.930 --> 00:00:25.840 
You remember the last story we saw?

11
00:00:26.090 --> 00:00:26.980 
Let's review it.

12
00:00:27.310 --> 00:00:31.220 
A diner at a high -end restaurant is
acting all high and mighty while ordering

13
00:00:31.230 --> 00:00:32.020 
food from the waiter.

14
00:00:32.670 --> 00:00:34.560 
Before serving the food, the waiter

15
00:00:34.570 --> 00:00:39.020 
secretly adds a pinch of salt, spits on
it, and then throws the chef under the bus.

16
00:00:39.650 --> 00:00:42.580 
The chef was sweating bullets, worried
he'd get the boot.

17
00:00:43.490 --> 00:00:44.980 
Now back to today's event.

18
00:00:45.590 --> 00:00:47.620 
What the waiter and the chef didn't know

19
00:00:47.630 --> 00:00:51.640 
is that the salty customer they once met
is the one who called the shots at the

20
00:00:51.650 --> 00:00:53.260 
restaurant and was testing his staff.

21
00:00:53.950 --> 00:00:56.180 
Both the waiter and the chef got the axe.

